atistics", "region": 0, "dims": [2, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 3, 1, 0], "bonus": 4, "penalty": 1, "note": "Self-taught to a working level (gratitude list). Pure compression; zero social or embodied payoff.", "fs": 29, "seed": 12}, "Economics": {"name": "Economics", "region": 0, "dims": [1, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 3, 2, 1], "bonus": 3, "penalty": 0, "note": "Reliable intellectual feed; markets thinking overlaps with work identity.", "fs": 34, "seed": 10}, "Forecasting & prediction": {"name": "Forecasting & prediction", "region": 0, "dims": [2, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 3, 2, 1], "bonus": 2, "penalty": 2, "note": "Fun compression with stakes, but flagged risk: analysis used to stay above uncertainty.", "fs": 36, "seed": 8}, "Bayesian reasoning": {"name": "Bayesian reasoning", "region": 0, "dims": [2, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 3, 1, 1], "bonus": 2, "penalty": 2, "note": "A tool he genuinely uses, but 'demanding certainty no one can give' is a named failure mode.", "fs": 28, "seed": 14}, "Cognitive bias": {"name": "Cognitive bias", "region": 0, "dims": [1, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 3, 1, 1], "bonus": 2, "penalty": 1, "note": "Compression about the mind's errors; thin on every load-bearing need but one.", "fs": 29, "seed": 13}, "Rationality": {"name": "Rationality", "region": 0, "dims": [2, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 3, 1, 1], "bonus": 2, "penalty": 3, "note": "Values page #1 is literally 'Presence over optimization.' The interest survives; the lifestyle version gets penalized.", "fs": 27, "seed": 15}, "Evolutionary mechanics": {"name": "Evolutionary mechanics", "region": 0, "dims": [1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 3, 1, 0], "bonus": 1, "penalty": 0, "note": "Deep cause-and-effect satisfaction, nothing else on the stack.", "fs": 22, "seed": 16}, "Long-distance trekking": {"name": "Long-distance trekking", "region": 1, "dims": [3, 1, 2, 3, 3, 2, 1, 3, 0], "bonus": 8, "penalty": 0, "note": "Completed the Appalachian Trail in 99 days; cited in Values, Gratitude, and Psych as proof he can do hard things. Maximum embodied agency.", "fs": 83, "seed": 1},